# TypeScript / React

- Prefer **explicit types** on exported APIs (`src/lib/` domain code especially).
- Keep **domain logic** (EMI, amortisation, PF tranches) **pure** and framework-free in `src/lib/`; React components orchestrate inputs and display.
- Use **Zod** for parsing user / URL / JSON inputs when you add those surfaces (spec §12).
- Avoid `any`; use `unknown` + narrowing for untrusted data.
